 ðŸšš Multi-Vehicle Delivery Route Visualizer

This project is a web-based tool that visualizes optimized delivery routes for multiple vehicles using Leaflet.js and OR-Tools.

The backend is written in javascipt and Python using Google OR-Tools. This frontend only shows a static JSON output (`routes4.json`) from that backend.

